Our menu ranged from local foods, western, pasta, coffee, ice blended drinks, desserts and more. We also provide services for events such as birthday parties, gathering, shooting, corporate events and live performance. Our Cafe is suitable for work and study. We have tons of weekly activities such as: Board Games, Card Games, Live Performance and Open Mic. Do give us a try and you will enjoy the environment and experience!
